\b0\fs38 \cf3 \cb1 In large bowl, beat 1 1/2 cups powdered sugar and the butter with electric mixer on medium speed,          or mix with spoon. Stir in vanilla, 1/2 teaspoon almond extract and the egg. Stir in flour, baking soda and cream of tartar. Cover and refrigerate about 2 hours or until firm.\
