\b0\fs38 \cf3 \cb1 Heat oven to 375\'b0F. On lightly floured cloth-covered surface, roll half of dough at a time 1/8 inch thick. Cut into desired shapes. On ungreased cookie sheets, place 2 inches apart. \
\ls1\ilvl0
